<template>
    <input type="text" ref="latLngRef" @input="$emit('update:latLng', $event.target.value)" :value="latLng" placeholder="Enter a place">
    <input type="text" ref="addRef" @input="$emit('update:add', $event.target.value)" :value="add" placeholder="Enter a place">
</template>



<script>

/* eslint-disable */

import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue';


export default {
    props:{
        add:{
            type: String,
            default: ''
        },
        latLng:{
            type: String,
            default: ''
        }
    },
    setup(){
        const addRef = ref();
        const latLngRef = ref();

        const options = {
            fields: ["formatted_address", "geometry"],
            strictBounds: false,
            types: ["establishment"],
        };

        onMounted(() => {
            input = addRef.value;
            const autocomplete = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(input, options);
            // autocomplete.bindTo("bounds", map);
            const place = autocomplete.getPlace();


            // const add = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(addRef.value, {
            //     types: ['address'],
            //     fields: ['address_components']
            // });

            // const autoCompleteLatLng = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(latLngRef.value, {
            //     types: ['geometry'],
            //     fields: ['address_components']
            // });
        })
        return { addRef, latLngRef }
    }
}
</script>
